item.title: How Do I Make And Add Custom Items TO My Server?
item.dc:creator: @9d_n_1_n_e 9d n 1 n e
item.description:
@9d_n_1_n_e wrote:

use bluurrs client and a delta base. best for new ppl + customs.
Get the ints for the model + download the .rar file of the model and add it into the models folder, go in-game and type ‘add model ####’ ‘####’ will be wat the model number will be
then just close ur client, compile and load it back up and you’re done.
